Input resolution & $1280 \times 720$ / $640 \times 480$ \\
Batch size & 2 (physical) $\times$ 8 (accumulation) \\
Effective batch & 16 \\
Optimizer & AdamW ($\beta_1{=}0.9, \beta_2{=}0.999$) \\
