Head LR & $5 \times 10^{-4}$ \\
Weight decay & $5 \times 10^{-2}$ (bias/norm excluded) \\
Scheduler & Warmup (2 ep) $\rightarrow$ OneCycleLR \\
Gradient clipping & $\ell_2$-norm $= 1.0$ \\
Precision & FP32 \\
EMA decay & 0.995 (from stage rf3) \\
Hardware & Single RTX 3060 (12 GB) \\
\bottomrule
\end{tabular}
\end{table}

